HEADWORD: Mnemonics
<hw>Mne*mon"ics</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <grk>ta~
mnhmonika`</grk>: cf. F. <ets>mn⟦eacute⟧monique</ets>.]</ety> <def>The
